project-fortidragon/
├─ README.md
├─ requirements.txt
├─ .gitignore
├─ .env.example                  # sample environment variables (no secrets)
├─ run.py                        # tiny runner (imports create_app and runs dev server)
├─ instance/                     # created by Flask (holds SQLite DB); git-ignored
│  └─ fortidragon.sqlite         # created by init script (not checked in)
├─ scripts/
│  ├─ init_db.py                 # creates tables & optional seed data
│  └─ seed_demo.py               # optional: seed a demo user & a sample report
├─ fortidragon/                  # application package
│  ├─ __init__.py                # app factory (create_app), config, blueprint registration
│  ├─ config.py                  # Config classes (Dev/Prod/Test), SQLite URI, SECRET_KEY from env
│  ├─ extensions.py              # db, login_manager, bcrypt, csrf instances
│  ├─ models.py                  # User, Report models (FK: Report.submitted_by -> User.id)
│  ├─ main/                      # “Index” + “About”
│  │  ├─ __init__.py
│  │  └─ routes.py               # / (dashboard), /about
│  ├─ auth/                      # register/login/logout
│  │  ├─ __init__.py
│  │  ├─ routes.py               # /register, /login, /logout
│  │  └─ forms.py                # RegisterForm, LoginForm (Flask-WTF)
│  ├─ reports/                   # submit form + list/detail
│  │  ├─ __init__.py
│  │  ├─ routes.py               # /reports, /reports/<id>, /reports/new (GET/POST)
│  │  └─ forms.py                # ReportForm (title, severity, description, CVE optional)
│  ├─ templates/
│  │  ├─ base.html               # Bootstrap layout, navbar, flash messages, blocks
│  │  ├─ macros.html             # small Jinja helpers (badges, form fields)
│  │  ├─ main/
│  │  │  ├─ index.html           # dashboard tiles + recent reports table
│  │  │  └─ about.html
│  │  ├─ auth/
│  │  │  ├─ login.html
│  │  │  └─ register.html
│  │  └─ reports/
│  │     ├─ list.html            # table of reports; filter by status/severity
│  │     ├─ detail.html          # ticket view; status updates (modal)
│  │     └─ form.html            # submit vulnerability (GET/POST)
│  └─ static/
│     ├─ css/
│     │  └─ custom.css           # optional tweaks on top of Bootstrap
│     ├─ js/
│     │  └─ app.js               # optional: toast init, modal handlers
│     └─ img/
│        └─ favicon.ico          # or a small dragon/shield icon
└─ tests/                        # optional but professional
   ├─ conftest.py
   └─ test_smoke.py
